'''Eureka Dome''' is a mountain in the [[Ogilvie Mountains]] of [[Yukon]], Canada.<ref>Natural Resources Canada. [http://geonames2.nrcan.gc.ca/cgi-bin/v9/sima_unique_v9?english?KADIO?C "Eureka Dome"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110608155536/http://geonames2.nrcan.gc.ca/cgi-bin/v9/sima_unique_v9?english%3FKADIO%3FC |date=2011-06-08 }}, geonames2.nrcan.gc.ca. Accessed March 14, 2009.</ref> The trail for the [[Yukon Quest]] 1,000-mile sled dog race passes over the mountain every February.
